   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Alterra Africa Accelerator Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Expected
development impact through:    

  (i)
job creation, improved job quality and diversity, and economic growth;    

  (ii)
at investee company level, implementing best practice corporate governance and
social and environmental standards; and    

  (iii)
supporting regional integration by investing in companies expanding into
neighboring countries.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project is an investment in Alterra Africa Accelerator Fund L.P., a Mauritian limited partnership (Alterra or Fund), which will invest in equity and equity-linked instruments in companies across Africa. The Fund will invest in companies in telecommunications, technology, financial services, consumer products &amp; services and infrastructure &amp; logistics sectors.</narrative>
  </description>
